{"word":"Joab","slug":"joab","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Joab</b> <a href=\"#/H3097\">H3097</a> <br/> 1. Son of David's sister<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=16'>1Ch 2:16</a> <br/> - Commander of David's army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=16'>2Sa 8:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=23'>2Sa 20:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=6'>1Ch 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=18&verse=15'>1Ch 18:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=34'>1Ch 27:34</a> <br/> - Dedicated spoils of his battles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=26&verse=28'>1Ch 26:28</a> <br/> - Defeated the Jebusites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=6'>1Ch 11:6</a> <br/> - Defeats and slays Abner<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=32'>2Sa 2:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=27'>2Sa 3:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=5'>1Ki 2:5</a> <br/> - Destroys all the males in Edom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=16'>1Ki 11:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=60&verse=1'>Psa 60:1</a> <br/> - Defeats the Ammonites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=10&verse=14'>2Sa 10:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=19&verse=15'>1Ch 19:15</a> <br/> - Captures Rabbah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=1'>2Sa 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=11&verse=25'>2Sa 11:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=29'>2Sa 12:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=2'>1Ch 20:2</a> <br/> - Procures the return of Absalom to Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=24'>2Sa 14:24</a> <br/> - Barley field of, burned by Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=14&verse=33'>2Sa 14:33</a> <br/> - Pursues and kills Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18'>2Sa 18</a> <br/> - Censures David for lamenting the death of Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=8'>2Sa 19:8</a> <br/> - Replaced by Amasa as commander of David's army<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=25'>2Sa 17:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=13'>2Sa 19:13</a> <br/> - Kills Amasa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=13'>2Sa 20:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=5'>1Ki 2:5</a> <br/> - Causes Sheba to be put to death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=22'>2Sa 20:22</a> <br/> - Opposes the numbering of the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=3'>2Sa 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=21&verse=3'>1Ch 21:3</a> <br/> Numbers the people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=9'>2Sa 24:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=21&verse=5'>1Ch 21:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=24'>1Ch 27:24</a><br/> - Supports Adonijah as successor to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=1&verse=7'>1Ki 1:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=28'>1Ki 2:28</a> <br/> - Slain by Benaiah, under Solomon's order<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=34'>1Ki 2:34</a> <br/> 2. A grandson of Kenaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=14'>1Ch 4:14</a><br/> 3. An Israelite (or the name of two Israelites) whose descendants returned from Babylon to Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=6'>Ezr 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=9'>Ezr 8:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=11'>Neh 7:11</a><br/> 4. &#187;House of Joab,&#171; probably identical with Joab, 1 above<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=54'>1Ch 2:54</a>"}]}